            <p>The information here is intended primarily for the personal viewing of our readers. It may not be duplicated, distributed, modified, publicly displayed, or used for commercial purposes in whole or in part without the prior expressed written permission of the Shingo Institute. If you would like to request permission to use an article, to republish material from any of the Shingo Institute publications, or to acquire other information from the Shingo Institute, please send a permission request to <a href="mailto:shingo.pr@usu.edu">shingo.pr@usu.edu</a>.</p>
        <h4>Changes to this Policy</h4>
            <p>We may occasionally update this privacy policy. When we do, we will revise the "last updated" date at the top of the privacy policy. For material changes to this privacy policy, we will notify you either by placing a prominent notice on the home page of our web site or by directly sending you a notification. We encourage you to periodically review this privacy policy to stay informed about how we are helping to protect the information we collect. Your continued use of the service constitutes your agreement to this privacy policy and any updates.</p>
